It&#039;s because [CDATA , but You can force tags to appear by using html instead.
For example [code=inline]&amp;lt;menu&amp;gt; Link &amp;lt;/menu&amp;gt; [/code]

The homepage has the white background because of this:

[prism].layout-homepage footer {
    background: white; 
    color: #222;
}[/prism]

The standard footer is black:
[prism]footer {
    padding: 25px 0;
    text-align: center;
    background: #222;
    color: #fff;
}[/prism]

So if you want to change this for other layout, then add:
[prism]
//white background
.layout-sidebar_right  footer {
    background: white; 
    color: #222;
}[/prism]

I thought you wanted white background everywhere.  

[prism]// black background for homepage
.layout-homepage footer {
    background: #222;
    color: #fff;
}[/prism]

